snippet.title: DisneyJuniorUK
snippet.description:
Welcome to the official Disney Junior UK YouTube channel! Disney Junior is the place where magical storytelling comes to life. Watch clips and get ready to sing-a-long to songs from your little one’s favourite shows including Vampirina, The Lion Guard, T.O.T.S., PJ Masks, Bluey, Mickey And The Roadster Racers, Puppy Dog Pals and more! ✨
 
This page is in place for our fans. However, we do need to have certain rules. Please be aware that we do not accept or consider unsolicited ideas submissions, and, also, we must reserve the right to remove any posting or other material that we find off-topic, inappropriate or objectionable. This page is targeted at fans who are over 13 years.
 
Comments do not represent the views of The Walt Disney Company. They are reactively moderated -- if you wish to report anything inappropriate, please email: feedback@disneyjunior.co.uk
